title: Bug 120315 - Display property 'none' not taking effect in new PDF emitter
OB: When the display property of an item is set to 'none', it does not take effect in the new PDF emitter.
EB: The display property 'none' should cause the item to be hidden or not rendered in the new PDF emitter.
SR: To reproduce the issue:1. Add a label.2. Open the 'Properties' view.3. Set the 'sectionDisplay' property to 'none'.
